{
  "text": "The following SR III (464 bp long) is represented by a unique AT-rich (33% GC) sequence. It contains the putative promoter region including the transcription initiation site (TIS) at the 3\u2032 end. A similar AT-rich region preceding the TIS has been found in Solanum [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , Nicotiana [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] , Capsicum [CITATION_6] and other plant species [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] [CITATION_9] .",
